trans-unit.source: Provides a component editor for the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.ParameterCollection"></xref> object that is specified by the <xref uid="langword_csharp_Parameters" name="Parameters" href=""></xref> properties of the associated data source control.
trans-unit.target: Inneholder en komponent redigeringsprogrammet for den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.ParameterCollection"> </xref> objektet som er angitt av den <xref uid="langword_csharp_Parameters" name="Parameters" href=""> </xref> egenskaper for de tilknyttede dataene kilde kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: The ParameterCollectionEditor class provides a user interface for editing the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Parameter> elements of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ParameterCollection> object at design time, as specified by one of the `Parameters` properties.
trans-unit.target: Klassen ParameterCollectionEditor gir et brukergrensesnitt for redigering av <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Parameter>elementer i den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ParameterCollection>objektet ved utformingen, som er angitt av én av den `Parameters` egenskaper.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ParameterCollection> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Parameter>

trans-unit.source: The `Parameters` properties include the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ObjectDataSource.DeleteParameters%2A>, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ObjectDataSource.FilterParameters%2A>, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ObjectDataSource.InsertParameters%2A>, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ObjectDataSource.SelectParameters%2A> and <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ObjectDataSource.UpdateParameters%2A> properties of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ObjectDataSource>, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.SqlDataSource>, and other data source controls.
trans-unit.target: Den `Parameters` egenskapene inkluderer den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ObjectDataSource.DeleteParameters%2A>, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ObjectDataSource.FilterParameters%2A>, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ObjectDataSource.InsertParameters%2A>, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ObjectDataSource.SelectParameters%2A>og <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ObjectDataSource.UpdateParameters%2A>egenskapene for den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ObjectDataSource>, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.SqlDataSource>, og andre datakilde-kontroller.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.SqlDataSource> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ObjectDataSource> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ObjectDataSource.UpdateParameters%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ObjectDataSource.SelectParameters%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ObjectDataSource.InsertParameters%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ObjectDataSource.FilterParameters%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ObjectDataSource.DeleteParameters%2A>

trans-unit.source: The ParameterCollectionEditor is invoked by selecting the ellipsis (**…**) button on one of the `Parameters` properties in the **Properties** grid of the visual designer.
trans-unit.target: ParameterCollectionEditor aktiveres ved å velge ellipsen (**... **) knapp i én av de `Parameters` egenskaper i den **Egenskaper** rutenett med den visuelle utformeren.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterCollectionEditor.EditValue%2A> method edits the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Parameter> elements of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ParameterCollection> for the associated data source control.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterCollectionEditor.EditValue%2A>metoden redigeringer i <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Parameter>elementer i den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ParameterCollection>for kontrollen som kilde tilknyttede data.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ParameterCollection> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Parameter> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterCollectionEditor.EditValue%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterCollectionEditor.GetEditStyle%2A> method gets the editing style that is associated with this editor.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterCollectionEditor.GetEditStyle%2A>metoden henter redigering stilen som er knyttet til dette redigeringsprogrammet.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterCollectionEditor.GetEditStyle%2A>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterCollectionEditor"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterCollectionEditor"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: The .NET Framework constructs a new instance of the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterCollectionEditor> class when the page designer selects the ellipsis (**…**) button on one of the `Parameters` properties in the visual designer's **Properties** grid while designing the associated data source control.
trans-unit.target: .NET Framework bygger en ny forekomst av klassen <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterCollectionEditor>når designer siden velger ellipsen (**... **) knapp i én av de `Parameters` egenskaper i den visuelle utformeren **Egenskaper** rutenett under utformer tilknyttede datakilde-kontroll.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterCollectionEditor>

trans-unit.source: Edits the elements of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.ParameterCollection"></xref> objects of the associated data source control.
trans-unit.target: Redigerer elementer i den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.ParameterCollection"> </xref> objekter av de tilknyttede dataene kilde kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: The EditValue method extracts the associated data source control and the data source control designer that is associated with that control from the `context` parameter.
trans-unit.target: Metoden EditValue trekker ut tilknyttede datakildekontrollen og datakilde kontrollen designer som er forbundet med denne kontrollen fra den `context` parameteren.

trans-unit.source: The supported data source controls include the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ObjectDataSource> and <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.SqlDataSource> controls, with their corresponding <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ObjectDataSourceDesigner> and <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.SqlDataSourceDesigner> designers.
trans-unit.target: Støttet datakildekontroller omfatter den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ObjectDataSource>og <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.SqlDataSource>Kontroller med tilhørende <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ObjectDataSourceDesigner>og <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.SqlDataSourceDesigner>utviklere.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.SqlDataSourceDesigner> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ObjectDataSourceDesigner> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.SqlDataSource> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ObjectDataSource>

trans-unit.source: Once the data is extracted, the EditValue calls back to the data source control designer to display an editing dialog box that is used to edit a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ParameterCollection> object that is referenced by one of the `Parameters` properties of the data source control.
trans-unit.target: Når dataene er trukket ut, EditValue kaller tilbake til den kontroll utformeren til å vise en redigering dialogboks som brukes til å redigere en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ParameterCollection>objektet som refereres av en av de `Parameters` egenskaper for kilde kontroll.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ParameterCollection>

trans-unit.source: An <xref href="System.ComponentModel.ITypeDescriptorContext"></xref> object used to acquire context information.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.ComponentModel.ITypeDescriptorContext"> </xref> objektet brukes til å hente informasjon om sikkerhetskontekst.

trans-unit.source: An object implementing the <xref:System.IServiceProvider> through which editing services can be obtained.
trans-unit.target: Et objekt som implementerer den <xref:System.IServiceProvider>som redigering services kan hentes.</xref:System.IServiceProvider>

trans-unit.source: The object to edit the value for.
trans-unit.target: Objektet til å redigere verdien for.

trans-unit.source: The new value; otherwise, if the value of the object has not changed, value unchanged.
trans-unit.target: Den nye value ; Ellers hvis verdien for objektet ikke er endret, value uendret.

trans-unit.source: value is .
trans-unit.target: valueis .

trans-unit.source: Gets the editing style that is associated with this editor.
trans-unit.target: Henter redigering stilen som er knyttet til dette redigeringsprogrammet.

trans-unit.source: The GetEditStyle method always returns the <xref:System.Drawing.Design.UITypeEditorEditStyle> value, which indicates that the user interface for the editor is a modal dialog box.
trans-unit.target: Metoden GetEditStyle returnerer alltid den <xref:System.Drawing.Design.UITypeEditorEditStyle>-verdi som angir at brukergrensesnittet for redigeringsprogrammet er en modal dialogboks.</xref:System.Drawing.Design.UITypeEditorEditStyle>

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.ComponentModel.ITypeDescriptorContext"></xref> object that indicates the context of the object being edited.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.ComponentModel.ITypeDescriptorContext"> </xref> objekt som angir konteksten for objektet som redigeres.

trans-unit.source: The editing style that is associated with this editor.
trans-unit.target: Redigering stilen som er knyttet til dette redigeringsprogrammet.
